National Museum 360 Viewer


REQUIREMENTS

    * nodejs


GETTING STARTED

    > git clone git@github.com:GuardianInteractive/national-museum-360.git
    > cd national-museum-360
    > npm install
    > grunt

DEVELOPER DEPENDENCIES

    * imagemagick
    * avconv (or ffmpeg)

EXTRACTING VIDEO FRAMES

    > avconv -i Lewis_Chessmen_Queen_00042.MTS -r 1 -vsync 1 -filter:v "crop=560:740:680:190" -qscale:v 1 -f image2 images/chess-%03d.png


RESIZE AND OPTIMIZE IMAGES

    > mogrify -path optimized/ -format jpg -unsharp 0.7x0.7+1+0 -strip -quality 70 ./images/*.png